      &lt;img alt="The Ryzen 9 9950X CPU" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/vcdddqaLl4Q_Ak9C4TJy-mscg-0=/417x0:3657x2160/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73648175/Ryzen_9000_7.0.png" /&gt;
